现代化物流
铁 道 运 输 与 经 济 RAILWAY TRANSPORT AND ECONOMY
文章编号：1003-1421(2019)05-0058-05     中图分类号：U169.6     文献标识码：A DOI：10.16668/j.cnki.issn.1003-1421.2019.05.11
集装箱海铁联运全程物流
服务发展对策研究
A Study on Developing Strategies of the Whole Process Logistics Service for Sea-rail Container Intermodal Transport
齐颖秀1，郎茂祥1，董  楠2，何  洁2，冯欲晓3
QI Yingxiu1，LANG Maoxiang1，DONG Nan2，HE Jie2，FENG Yuxiao3
（1. 北京交通大学 交通运输学院，北京  100044；2. 中铁集装箱运输有限责任公司 多式联运部， 北京  100055；3. 昆明铁道职业技术学院 运输系，云南 昆明  650011）
(1.School of Traffic and Transportation, Beijing Jiaotong University, Beijing 100044, China；2.Department of Intermodal Transportation, China Railway Container Transportation Co., Ltd., Beijing 100055, China；3.College of
Transport, Kunming Railway Vocational Technical College, Kunming 650011, Yunnan, China)
摘  要：集装箱海铁联运的发展有利于推进运输结构调整 、促进区域外向型经济 发展 ，然而我国铁路承担港口货物的集散比例较低 ，海铁联运服务仍停留在单纯 的运输服务上 。概述我国集装箱海铁联运发展现状 ，针对存在的全程服务过程缺 乏统筹协调 、海铁联运港站分离 、运输服务标准和规范不协调等问题 ，从设计集 装箱海铁联运全程物流服务方案 、加强集装箱海铁联运场站建设 、构建集装箱海 铁联运沟通协调机制 、掌握集装箱海铁联运经营主动权 、明确集装箱海铁联运多 方职责等方面提出促进我国集装箱海铁联运全程物流服务发展的对策 。 关键词：多式联运；全程物流；服务流程；外贸货物；货运代理
Abstract: The development of container sea-rail intermodal transport is conducive to the adjustment of transport structure and the promotion of regional export-oriented economic development. However, railway transportation only covers a small part of port cargo distribution, and sea-rail intermodal transport services still remain on pure transportation services. This paper outlines the development status of container rail-sea intermodal transport in China. In view of the existing problems such as lack of overall coordination in the whole service process, separation of port and station, inconsistency of transport service standards and norms, this paper puts forward some countermeasures to promote the development of logistics service of container sea-rail intermodal transport in China from the aspects of designing the logistics service scheme for container sea-rail intermodal transport, strengthening the construction of container sea-rail intermodal terminal, constructing the communication and coordination mechanism for container sea-rail intermodal transport, grasping the initiative of container sea-rail intermodal transport operation, and defining the multi-responsibilities of container sea-rail intermodal transport. Keywords: Multi-modal Transportation; Whole Process Logistics; Service Procedure; Foreign Trade Cargo; Freight Forwarders
